"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.5.7\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.5.7</span> 標題：金牌、額頭上的飾物（forehead plate, forehead ornament）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צִיץ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tsits)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36\">EXO 28:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:30\">EXO 39:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:9\">LEV 8:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： στέφανος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： stefanos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir45:12\">SIR 45:12</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0051_highpriest_foreheadplate.png\" alt=\"OAI-0051_highpriest_foreheadplate\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>大祭司要在前額上、禮冠的下方戴一條類似頭帶的飾物，稱為金牌。金牌由兩種材料做成。前面是一塊薄金片，錘打成窄帶子的形狀，上面刻著「歸耶和華為聖」。牌的末端繫著藍色的絲帶或線繩，線繩在頭後打結，將金牌固定在前額上。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>對於<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36\">EXO 28:36</a> 中的希伯來文<em>tsits</em> ，我們查閱的10個英文譯本有多達8種譯法。「窄帶子」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直譯）或「小牌子」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 直譯）等類似譯法可能是最好的。另外也可譯作「金頭帶」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:9\">LEV 8:9</a> 有一個字面意為「金花，聖冠」的表達，第一個詞語中的「花」譯自希伯來文<em>tsits</em> ，意思可能是「盛開的花」或「花朵」（如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:23\">NUM 17:23</a> 中的意思，希伯來文本是第23節；《和》17:8），或「閃亮的東西」。當這個詞與限定詞「金的」一起使用時，很多英文譯本都將其解作“plate”（「牌」），如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 。然而，也有譯本譯作「花形金飾」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 直譯），或簡單地譯作「金花」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 直譯）。但是，在希伯來文本中，「金花」與「聖冠」並列，並且是由「聖冠」來解釋的。「聖冠」顯然不是指象徵皇室的王冠。譯作「冠」的希伯來文詞語也可以表示「奉獻」，整個語句大概表示金牌是大祭司奉獻給上帝的象徵。有學者提出，「聖冠」可以譯作「表明亞倫被奉獻給上帝的記號」。整個語句可以譯作：「表明亞倫被奉獻給上帝的金物件。」</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
